### **1. UserBean.java (ì¡°ì§ ëª©ë¡ ë¶ˆëŸ¬ì˜¤ê¸°)**
```java
@ManagedBean
@ViewScoped
public class UserBean {
    private String organization;
    private List<SelectItem> organizationList;

    @PostConstruct
    public void init() {
        loadOrganizationList();
    }

    public void loadOrganizationList() {
        organizationList = new ArrayList<>();
        organizationList.add(new SelectItem("", "ì „ì²´")); // "ì „ì²´" ì„ íƒ ì¶”ê°€

        List<Group> groups = groupService.getAllOrganizations(); // DBì—ì„œ ê·¸ë£¹ ì •ë³´ ê°€ì ¸ì˜¤ê¸°
        for (Group group : groups) {
            organizationList.add(new SelectItem(group.getOrgCode(), group.getOrgName() + " (" + group.getOrgCode() + ")"));
        }
    }

    // Getter & Setter
    public String getOrganization() {
        return organization;
    }

    public void setOrganization(String organization) {
        this.organization = organization;
    }

    public List<SelectItem> getOrganizationList() {
        return organizationList;
    }
}
```
